name: JAM
description: Jam is a community for creators that started in Farcaster. Following our recent success of motivating better engagement in Farcaster joined by over 370 channel moderators, we are conducting an AI experimentation that will bring more people onchain and build communities through JamAI. Jam AI is an intelligent cyber squirrel that helps people with their creation. Collectively, we will build a future where humans and AI agents coexist and co-create.
